Public Attributes
UgiBatteryInfo Struct Reference

Overview

Battery data.

Public Attributes

BOOL canScan
 YES if battery is capable of scanning.
 
BOOL externalPowerIsConnected
 YES if external power is connected.
 
BOOL isCharging
 YES if battery is charging.
 
BOOL temperatureAtOrAboveThreshold
 YES if temperature is at or above the threshold for scanning.
 
BOOL temperatureWithin5DegreesOfThreshold
 YES if temperature is within 5 degrees C of the threshold for scanning.
 
BOOL temperatureWithin10DegreesOfThreshold
 YES if temperature is within 10 degrees C of the threshold for scanning.
 
BOOL temperatureWithin20DegreesOfThreshold
 YES if temperature is within 20 degrees C of the threshold for scanning.
 
int minutesRemaining
 Minutes of scanning remaining.
 
int percentRemaining
 Percent of scanning time remaining. This is not very accurate while charging.
 
double voltage
 Battery voltage.
